title: Zatch Bell (Konjiki no Gash!!) Revamped [NEW Fan Translation]
description: Every 1,000 years, 100 demon children are sent to Earth to compete in a battle to become King of the Demon World. Each demon is paired with a human partner who is given a spell book of a specific color. The human can then use the book to draw out the demon's latent powers. If a demon's book is burned, they disappear and return to the Demon World, relinquishing all right to the title of King. The last demon remaining will claim the crown. The series is oriented around Gash Bell and his human partner, Kiyomaro Takamine.
author: Makoto Raiku
